---
title: Black Bean Chilli & Garlic Rice Bowl with Cucumber & Radish Salsa
description: Say hello to the king of veggie bowls! There's nutrient-packed black beans that are wholesome and filling, garlic rice
and a cucumber-radish salsa, we bow before the might of this dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64cb1d359d7f792fbb6d0ac7-4c6f01ab.jpeg
